{
  "stem": "6076.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But this was my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was always busy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not just doing his job, by doing, you know, his job, but always busy endlessly taking care of people, thinking about if somebody got sick, you know, giving him a visit and if the [INAUDIBLE] was taking place according to the orthodox way.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If a special man or woman died who was very orthodox-- special orthodox-- they gave him special privilege, these men, to do according to the-- to the Jewish law, you know, not to fail with anything.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So my father was busy with those things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, of course, my mother was busy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "On the other hand, she was busy in her way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She was busy crocheting, doing cooking, washing the dishes, [? knitting ?,] cleaning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Like I say, both of them kept busy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And if it was an evening in the winter, when it was cold-- like, you know, we didn't go no place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My father would sit down and play [INAUDIBLE] with his partner, the other shochet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he will enjoy that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I would walk over to the table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I would say, Daddy, put the king here or put the queen here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he would say, don't tell me what to do!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Look-- she's learning already the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I was a little girl, I used to love it-- the way they were moving the kings and the queens, this and that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was always busy, and because-- and besides, spending time [NON-ENGLISH], learning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This was the most ritual thing for Hasidic people to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If I'm Hasidic boys, they spent hours learning in the [NON-ENGLISH], you know, for a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That kept them busy, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older sister Tobcha, she was a beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
